text: Ani amhi musa yanna tisa ratrinca vayada dila ani daha adhika ratrinni to purna kela, asa prakare tyancya palanakartyaca avadhi purna calisa ratrinca jhala ani musa, apala bha'u harunala mhanale, mi (gelya) nantara ya (lokam) ci vyavastha rakha ani sudharana karita raha ani upadravi va utpati lokancya margace anusarana karu naka
